																<div class="newscontent"><span style="font-size: 16px;">We are please to announce the " Let Talent Shine; Fundraising Variety Show Cum Music Marathon by Catholic Diocesan Schools 2025", an event oraganized to support the construction of new churches by the Catholic Diocese of Hong Kong, highlight our church's mission and spread the Gospel. This joint school event will also showcase the diverse talents of our students.</span>

